# Copy to .env.local.
#
# Auth: the /api/generate route uses the Claude Agent SDK, which authenticates via
# Claude Code's credentials. To run on a Pro/Max subscription token:
#   export CLAUDE_CODE_OAUTH_TOKEN=...      (e.g. from `claude setup-token`)
# and ensure ANTHROPIC_API_KEY is NOT set (it takes precedence over the OAuth token).
# Alternatively, set ANTHROPIC_API_KEY to use a pay-as-you-go Console key.
#
# Optional: override the model (defaults to claude-sonnet-4-6).
# DASHBOARD_MODEL=claude-sonnet-4-6
#
# Optional: run the full loop with a deterministic stub — no model call, no spend.
# MOCK_LLM=1
